metadata.title: Dogline Soft and Padded Comfort Microfiber Round Slip Lead for Dogs, Brown (W3/8" L60)
features: Rivetless Design, 9 colors and 4 sizes available
Two-ply, super soft, padded design for comfront
Strong and Durable; Reinforced with nylon webbing
description: These microfiber slip leads/kennel leashes bring together simplicity and elegance thanks to their elaborate workmanship. These slip leads/kennel leashes are perfect to handle dogs of different sizes with the same leash. Our leather leashes are available in 12 beautiful and rich colors from classy red to gorgeous purple. All leashes are hand-made and stitched with wax thread. This lead is suitable for any breed and size of dog. Go ahead, make your neighbors jealous. These round microfiber leashes are very soft yet very durable. They will not stretch or not break. Our European technology features nylon cord wrapped in microfiber.
